      <section eId="sec_6811_D">
        <num>6811-D</num>
        <heading>Notification of permanent pharmacy discontinuance</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>be provided, to the extent possible, to customers who have had a\nprescription filled at the pharmacy within the year prior to its\ndiscontinuance through the customer's primary means of communication\nwith such pharmacy; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>be conspicuously posted at or adjacent to the place in the\npharmacy where prescriptions are presented for compounding and\ndispensing, in the waiting area for customers, or the area where\nprescribed drugs are dispensed.\n  2. The notification required pursuant to subdivision one of this\nsection shall include, but not be limited to:\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the date of such pharmacy's discontinuance;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the names, addresses, and phone numbers of the five nearest\npharmacies, including independently owned pharmacies, if applicable;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>instructions on transferring any existing prescriptions to another\npharmacy; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_6811_D__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>information regarding the disposition of prescription records if a\ncustomer fails to transfer a prescription prior to such pharmacy's\ndiscontinuance.\n  * NB Effective February 10, 2026\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
